data.text:
Hearts Desire, Ottawa, ON, Canada

Latitude and longitude coordinates are: 45.266609, -75.716660.

Hearts Desire is a small district located to the south of Ottawa, Ontario, the capital city of Canada. It is situated about 3 miles of the city center and is a very quiet small neighborhood, with the population close to 4,500 people. It is bordered by Nepean area to the north. Hearts Desire is a very comfortable and prestigious area to live, with quite expensive real estate.
